Sargonnas is not very nice, not like Paladine anyway. But he can't be as bad as Takhisis, cause she lives in the Abyss! Oh, and he likes minotaurs alot!
 - Kender Child explaining Krynn mythology</p>
Sargonnas dwells in Chamada, the second Layer of Gehenna. His Realm is called the Palace of Deception.</p>
Relationships
Sargonnas has two children with Takhisis, Nuitari and Zeboim.
Sources: Dragonlance Adventures, Dragonlance Campaign Setting (Third Edition), On Hallowed Ground